Detailed Description

cvmx_mix::_ctl

MIX_CTL = MIX Control Register

Description: NOTE: To write to the MIX_CTL register, a device would issue an IOBST directed at the MIO. To read the MIX_CTL register, a device would issue an IOBLD64 directed at the MIO.
